        <text>
                <body>
                        <div type="writingAct">
                                <opener><dateline sameAs="MBDatumszeile"><pb/> Modena
                                                Villas.<lb/>March 18<hi rendition="#sup">th</hi>
                                                1866.</dateline><salute sameAs="MBAnrede">My dear
                                                Dada,</salute></opener>
                                <p sameAs="MBTextohneEinzug"><seg type="comment"><orig>As <persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000003074">Jenny</persName> is
                                                  going to write to you</orig><note xml:id="b75caa46-13d0-43e8-bfd2-7ae808514c5a">Ein
                                                  Brief konnte nicht ermittelt werden.</note></seg>
                                        I may as well inclose a short letter. <seg type="comment"><orig>Your first adventure is very
                                                  amusing.</orig><note xml:id="b6cfef46-e66c-4e7c-8a3d-9032cf1bf857">Siehe <ref target="B00067/#start_sh3_w5g_4z">Marx
                                                  an J. Marx,
                                                  16.3.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170413T161430+0200" comment="{{Br. 63.4–26}}"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>.</note></seg>
                                        That you took a <hi rendition="#u">deaf</hi>
                                        <pb/> man for <hi rendition="#u">blind</hi> is capital. I
                                        wonder <seg type="comment"><orig>the “ears of the deaf were
                                                  not unstopped”</orig><note xml:id="f7f205f1-cc1e-46ae-844c-0bb360aeaeac">Nach
                                                  der Bibel. Das Alte Testament. Der Prophet Jesaja
                                                  35, 5. (((lDie_Bibel))) </note></seg> at your
                                        arrival&#160;… I can quite understand your having felt <hi rendition="#u">shy</hi> at being left alone with a
                                        deaf man, who was blind.</p>
                                <p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">Now Dr. Karl Marx of bad philosophy I
                                        hope <pb/>
                                        <seg type="comment"><orig>you will keep your promise and
                                                  come on Thursday.</orig><note xml:id="c4352e1c-3442-4579-a1ab-3d87cb7d09ae">Marx
                                                  besuchte Donnerstag, den 22.&#160;März 1866 eine
                                                  Feier seiner Töchter in London. Siehe auch <ref target="B00075/#start_xxs_dvg_4z">Marx an Engels,
                                                  24.3.<?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20170413T161743+0200" comment="{{Br. 72.17–24}}"?>1866<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>.</note></seg>
                                        So with love good-bye and believe me Your affectionate</p>
                                <closer sameAs="MBUnterschrift"><signed>Ellie. </signed></closer>
                        </div>
                </body>
